## 🛠️ Step-by-Step Installation & Setup
### 1. Clone & Initialize Environment
```bash
git clone [https://github.com/yourusername/R8-Earn.git](https://github.com/yourusername/R8-Earn.git)
cd R8-Earn

```
### 2. Configure Virtual Environment & Dependencies
```bash
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # On Windows use: venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt

```
### 3. Establish Local Parameters Configuration
Copy .env.example to create a working .env file:
```bash
cp .env.example .env

```
Open .env and fill in your custom production variables:
 * Set TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN using the token received from @BotFather.
 * Update SECRET_KEY with a unique cryptographically safe random key.
### 4. Boot Local Development Micro-Server
```bash
python main.py

```
The application will spin up at http://localhost:8000. Database schema tables are generated automatically on the initial engine startup.
