### 🗄️ Switching to PostgreSQL (Production Scaling)
To swap from SQLite to a highly concurrently scalable PostgreSQL database cluster pool instances:
 1. Provision a PostgreSQL node database service on your hosting provider platform.
 2. Modify the database URL string argument structure within your environment variable layer settings to use the secure asynchronous network path:
   ```ini
   DATABASE_URL="postgresql+asyncpg://db_user:db_pass@host_url:5432/db_name"
   
   ```
The backend database abstraction layers handle driver mapping adaptations cleanly without code restructuring changes.
